===Quotes===
*'''1977''': ''Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope''
**[[Obi-Wan Kenobi]]: "Vader was '''seduced''' by the [[dark side]] of the [[Force]]."
*'''1983''': ''Star Wars Episode VI: Return of the Jedi''
**[[Obi-Wan Kenobi]]: "Your father was '''seduced''' by the dark side of the Force.  He ceased to be Anakin Skywalker and became [[Darth Vader]]."

